OL,3,CCocktail of chemicals found in
OL,4,Cwaterways - how polluted is your local
OL,5,Criver?
OL,7,FAn ITV News investigation has revealed
OL,8,Fthe scale of pollution in England's
OL,9,Fwaterways, and it's not just sewage,
OL,10,Fas ITV News Health and Science
OL,11,FCorrespondent Martin Stew reports
OL,13,FA cocktail of almost 500 different
OL,14,Fchemicals, some of which are banned
OL,15,Fand almost half of which are classed
OL,16,Fas "very toxic" or "harmful", have
OL,17,Fbeen found in English waters.
OL,19,FOne of the substances found in
OL,20,FEngland's waterways was a banned,
OL,21,Fcarcinogenic "forever chemical".
