OL,7,FAlso among the chemicals discovered
OL,8,Fwere cocaine, ketamine and caffeine.
OL,10,FThe survey of more than 170 river and
OL,11,Fgroundwater catchments has been
OL,12,Fanalysed by Watershed Investigations
OL,13,Fon behalf of ITV News.
OL,15,FEnvironmental groups have called
OL,16,Fchemical pollution a silent killer in
OL,17,Four waterways and experts have likened
OL,18,Fone of the pollutants, Imidacloprid,
OL,19,Fto "novichok for insects".
