OL,7,FProfessor Dave Goulson, Sussex
OL,8,FUniversity, said: "A single teaspoon
OL,9,Fof this pesticide is enough to deliver
OL,10,Fa lethal dose to 1.25 billion honey
OL,11,Fbees. It's concerning that our rivers
OL,12,Fshould be awash with a potent
OL,13,Finsecticide."
OL,15,FThe most widespread chemicals found
OL,16,Fare classic markers of road runoff.
OL,17,FFarm runoff was another major source
OL,18,Fof contamination.
